  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join US</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/906418ea5b74ea7a1db50c8e47332d62.avif?t=1737037564\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br>Join our <strong>Discord</strong> to stay updated about the development of the game and come <strong>share your ideas with us!</strong> You can also participate in some of the organized <strong>Twitch Lives!</strong> Who knows, maybe <strong>your kills</strong> and <strong>your name</strong> in the killfeed will appear in a future trailer? (all links are on the right side of the Steam Page!)</p><br><h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/f703a3d65d47e7013bba5beda744d8e7.avif?t=1737037564\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras_big/f703a3d65d47e7013bba5beda744d8e7.avif?t=1737037564 width=800 height=450 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/148f35e251a1e7ec09e537cf68a8ac79.avif?t=1737037564\" width=650 height=146 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BattleHeights is a <strong>multiplayer Heroic Fantasy fast-paced action game.</strong> Choose your <strong>class,</strong> use your <strong>double jump,</strong> leap from cloud to cloud like an eagle in dizzying battles where the <strong>void becomes as perilous as it is strategic!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/b0cebb90fb364d530782d4c57d882031.avif?t=1737037564\" width=596 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/e2927b6cdb1c4bb512f7883438ca26f0.avif?t=1737037564\" width=605 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You want some game modes? We have some game modes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch, Capture the Zone... We got some <strong>classic modes</strong> from multiplayer games that everybody loves, but some <strong>originals</strong> too, like, for example, Grappling Race and Rug-Bomb!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Rug-Bomb</strong>, you have to snatch the <strong>precious gem</strong> like a rugby ball <i>(by gem, we literally mean a bomb)</i>, zigzag through opponents <i>(or wreck them, it's more fun)</i> and give them a taste of the <strong>heat</strong> by blowing up their base! <i>(don't stay close of the blast, you could get hurt)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/fa853149da65ba5d0e46708098f265bc.avif?t=1737037564\" width=607 height=283 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/148f35e251a1e7ec09e537cf68a8ac79.avif?t=1737037564\" width=650 height=146 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BattleHeights is a <strong>multiplayer Heroic Fantasy fast-paced action game.</strong> Choose your <strong>class,</strong> use your <strong>double jump,</strong> leap from cloud to cloud like an eagle in dizzying battles where the <strong>void becomes as perilous as it is strategic!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/b0cebb90fb364d530782d4c57d882031.avif?t=1737037564\" width=596 height=330 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/1f6647681fa092c54adec3ff2320a715.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/e2927b6cdb1c4bb512f7883438ca26f0.avif?t=1737037564\" width=605 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/cdd6a1b38f3156d51ab0ddda65d13821.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You want some game modes? We have some game modes!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deathmatch and Team Deathmatch, Capture the Zone... We got some <strong>classic modes</strong> from multiplayer games that everybody loves, but some <strong>originals</strong> too, like, for example, Grappling Race and Rug-Bomb!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Rug-Bomb</strong>, you have to snatch the <strong>precious gem</strong> like a rugby ball <i>(by gem, we literally mean a bomb)</i>, zigzag through opponents <i>(or wreck them, it's more fun)</i> and give them a taste of the <strong>heat</strong> by blowing up their base! <i>(don't stay close of the blast, you could get hurt)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/fa853149da65ba5d0e46708098f265bc.avif?t=1737037564\" width=607 height=283 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.poster.avif?t=1737037564\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.webm?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2932940/extras/c9a27d150c27076a16ca08d3cdeb4adf.mp4?t=1737037564\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
